<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to HosAlivio</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #FBF9F5; margin: 0; padding: 32px 16px; color: #1D1C1A;">
  <table align="center" width="100%" style="max-width: 520px; background: white; border: 1px solid #EFECE6; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 28px 32px 8px;">
        <div style="display: inline-block; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: #D97757; color: white; text-align: center; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold;">♡</div>
        <h1 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">You've been added to <%= @patient.first_name %>'s care team.</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6B665F; margin: 0;">HosAlivio Hospice · <%= @patient.agency&.name %></p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 0 32px 16px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55;">
        <p>Hi <%= @user.full_name.to_s.split.first %>,</p>
        <p>
          <%= @invited_by.full_name %> at <%= @patient.agency&.name %> has set up a secure family portal
          so you can reach the care team looking after <strong><%= @patient.full_name %></strong> anytime.
        </p>
        <p>You can send messages, report symptom changes, and read updates from every discipline (RN, MD, social worker, chaplain) in one place.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 0 32px 16px;">
        <div style="background: #FBF9F5; border: 1px solid #EFECE6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px;">
          <div style="font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #6B665F; font-weight: bold;">How to sign in</div>
          <div style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px;">No password to remember. Open the family portal and enter your email:</div>
          <div style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px;">Email: <strong><%= @user.email %></strong></div>
          <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6B665F; margin-top: 8px;">We'll email you a 6-digit code to sign in. The code expires in 15 minutes.</div>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 32px 28px; text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= new_passwordless_url %>"
           style="display: inline-block; background: #D97757; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;">
          Open the family portal
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 0 32px 24px; border-top: 1px solid #EFECE6;">
        <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #6B665F; margin: 16px 0 0; line-height: 1.5;">
          This is a secure clinical channel. If you received this in error, please email the agency and ignore this message.
          For emergencies, dial 911.
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
